The next thing to do is to  fill other fields. 
Make a meaningful name of the game. 
Write some hints to  potential explorers. 
You can also provide a picture as a hint. 
Here comes the  most important thing: you use a rich text editor to edit all the contents of  the QR code, that is the chain of clues. 
After all these steps, click the  "Launch" button and you will see a series of QR codes in a new page. 
